    "The surface protection, the microstructure design and the characterization of Li/Si anode are critical research topics to enable the successful utilization of these high energy density anodes 30.",
    "For example, Honrao et al.",
    "47 employ high-throughput screening and interpretable ML to obtain Li-containing compounds as surface protection compounds possessing high ionic conductivity and good stability such as Li 9 S 3 N, LiAlB 2 O 5, LiYO 2, LiSbF 4 and Sr 4 Li(BN2) 3 based on 15,000 candidates from MP.",
    "In terms of the Si anode, the large volume expansion during lithiation of the Si anode causes mechanical failures of the battery with rapid capacity decay and enhanced internal resistance 50.",
    "Thus, anode morphological characterization and in-situ simulation based on ML techniques have attained much attention on the anode side."
